About The Project

This is a simple fire simulation project and serves as my very first milestone in programming. Developed entirely on a mobile device, this project was born out of pure curiosity and a passion for understanding how visual elements are rendered through code.

Tech Stack & Methodology

     • Language: C++

     • Platform: Mobile-developed (Proof  that you can code anywhere!)

     • Learning Path: 100% Self-taught.

